Javier_shark006 Shop - E-commerce Platform for Digital Products

A modern, full-featured e-commerce platform built with Next.js 13, Supabase, and Tailwind CSS.

Features:
- Product management with image upload (up to 4 images)
- Category management
- Search and filtering
- Product variations
- WhatsApp order integration
- Admin dashboard
- Mobile-responsive design
- Feature guides for users
- Secure authentication

Tech Stack:
- Framework: Next.js 13.5.1
- Database: Supabase PostgreSQL
- Storage: Supabase Storage
- Auth: Supabase Auth
- UI: Shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS
- Icons: Lucide React
- Forms: React Hook Form + Zod
- Fonts: System fonts (native)
